53
00:05:45,134 --> 00:05:46,177
{\an8}FACULTY'S OFFICE

54
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:48,971
{\an8}About the four-panel manga for next week,

55
00:05:49,555 --> 00:05:51,807
can I give one slot to Kyomoto?

56
00:05:52,391 --> 00:05:55,019
