69
00:06:51,867 --> 00:06:55,663
MIKA THE SCHEMER BY FUJINO
AFTER SCHOOL BY KYOMOTO

70
00:07:01,752 --> 00:07:03,712
These are pro-level drawings.

71
00:07:03,796 --> 00:07:05,423
