73
00:07:08,259 --> 00:07:09,968
She's the truant kid, right?

74
00:07:12,888 --> 00:07:14,390
But, you know,

75
00:07:14,473 --> 00:07:18,936
compared to Kyomoto's drawings,
yours look pretty average.

76
00:07:33,451 --> 00:07:36,870
Fujino, how come
you're so good at drawing?

77
00:07:38,497 --> 00:07:41,625
You have the best drawing skills
out of all my students.

78
00:07:43,502 --> 00:07:46,339
You could become an artist
with these skills.

79
00:07:49,133 --> 00:07:52,803
Compared to Kyomoto's drawings,
yours look pretty average.

80
00:08:05,566 --> 00:08:06,900
I see.

81
00:08:07,943 --> 00:08:13,657
Kyomoto must be practicing drawing
while I go to school.

82
00:08:21,874 --> 00:08:24,668
A fourth grader who's better
at drawing than me?

83
00:08:24,752 --> 00:08:26,837
Absolutely unacceptable!

84
00:08:31,425 --> 00:08:33,677
HOW TO GET BETTER AT DRAWING

85
00:08:34,262 --> 00:08:35,388
Welcome.

86
00:08:38,266 --> 00:08:39,558
Thank you.

87
00:08:43,937 --> 00:08:44,980
