00:10:13,527 --> 00:10:15,153
Let's go hang out somewhere.

93
00:10:15,237 --> 00:10:16,364
Wanna come to my place?

94
00:10:16,447 --> 00:10:17,948
Yeah! Are you sure?

95
00:10:20,158 --> 00:10:21,410
Fujino.

96
00:10:21,994 --> 00:10:23,287
