97
00:10:26,874 --> 00:10:27,875
Hey.

98
00:10:28,459 --> 00:10:29,877
A human skeleton.

99
00:10:31,295 --> 00:10:33,881
Hey, we're sixth graders now, you know?

100
00:10:35,758 --> 00:10:39,470
We'll be in middle school next year.
Are you still gonna draw then?

101
00:10:40,137 --> 00:10:41,096
What?

102
00:10:41,764 --> 00:10:42,765
Yeah.

103
00:10:43,349 --> 00:10:45,100
I see.

104
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,811
You know what?

105
00:10:47,895 --> 00:10:50,523
Yosshi and Mihorin haven't
been able to tell you this either,

106
00:10:51,774 --> 00:10:54,943
