too old to keep drawing?

107
00:11:00,783 --> 00:11:04,703
You don't hang out with us anymore.

108
00:11:04,787 --> 00:11:07,581
Even when you do,
you're always drawing and you don't talk.

109
00:11:07,665 --> 00:11:08,666
Not to mention,

110
00:11:09,291 --> 00:11:11,585
if you keep drawing in middle school,

111
00:11:11,669 --> 00:11:14,588
people will think you're
a creepy <i>otaku</i>, you know?

112
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,216
Kae, can we go now?

113
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,134
Coming!

114
00:11:19,927 --> 00:11:21,053
Wait for me!

115
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:24,973
Stop bothering her. She's drawing, right?

116
00:11:31,772 --> 00:11:34,149
