Geez!

119
00:11:38,362 --> 00:11:39,655
Sheesh!

120
00:11:39,738 --> 00:11:41,239
Okay, okay.

121
00:11:41,323 --> 00:11:42,157
KNOCK FIRST

122
00:11:46,745 --> 00:11:50,332
How long are you gonna keep drawing manga?

123
00:11:52,084 --> 00:11:54,294
You should join my karate class.

124
00:11:54,378 --> 00:11:55,963
