134
00:12:45,262 --> 00:12:46,138
TEACHER

135
00:12:46,221 --> 00:12:47,139
HA HA HA HA

136
00:12:47,222 --> 00:12:49,224
HE ALSO NERVOUSLY TOUCHES HIS HAIR.
